<reference id="dlentry" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>dlentry</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>In a definition list, each list item is defined by the definition
list entry (&lt;dlentry&gt;) element. The definition list entry element includes
a term &lt;dt&gt; and one or more definitions or descriptions &lt;dd&gt; of that
term.</shortdesc>
